# React / TypeScript Rules

- Functional components only + hooks
- TypeScript strict: Interfaces for props/state
- Tailwind CSS for styling (utility-first)
- Board: SVG or Konva.js for draggable pawns/tiles
- Actions: Modal reveal for prompts, timer optional
- Consent UI: Prominent skip/safe-word button
- Video: Grid layout around board, responsive

Use useContext or Zustand for light global state (outside boardgame.io).
Memoize expensive components (React.memo, useMemo).
